sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as Istio Ingress Gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Activator as Knative Activator<br/>8012/TCP mTLS
    participant QueueProxy as Queue Proxy<br/>(sidecar)
    participant Caikit as Caikit Runtime<br/>(transformer-container)
    participant TGIS as TGIS Backend<br/>(kserve-container)<br/>8033/TCP gRPC
    participant Storage as Model Storage<br/>(S3 / PVC)
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus<br/>(User Workload Monitoring)

    rect rgb(220, 240, 255)
        Note over Client,Storage: Flow 1: HTTP Inference Request
        Client->>Gateway: POST /api/v1/task/text-generation<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (optional)
        Gateway->>Activator: Forward request<br/>HTTP/8012 mTLS<br/>Auth: Istio PeerAuthentication
        Activator->>QueueProxy: Route to pod<br/>mTLS
        QueueProxy->>Caikit: HTTP/8080<br/>mTLS (Istio sidecar)<br/>Auth: PeerAuthentication STRICT
        Caikit->>TGIS: gRPC/8033 (localhost)<br/>Plaintext (loopback)<br/>Auth: None
        Note over TGIS,Storage: Model loaded from /mnt/models/
        TGIS->>Storage: Load model artifacts<br/>Filesystem (PVC) or HTTPS/443 (S3)<br/>Auth: AWS IAM / Secret
        Storage-->>TGIS: Model weights
        TGIS-->>Caikit: Inference result (gRPC)
        Caikit-->>QueueProxy: JSON response
        QueueProxy-->>Activator: Response
        Activator-->>Gateway: Response
        Gateway-->>Client: JSON response (HTTPS)
    end

    rect rgb(220, 255, 220)
        Note over Client,Storage: Flow 2: gRPC Inference Request
        Client->>Gateway: gRPC TextGeneration<br/>HTTPS(h2)/443 TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (optional)
        Gateway->>Activator: Forward request<br/>gRPC/8012 mTLS<br/>Auth: Istio PeerAuthentication
        Activator->>QueueProxy: Route to pod<br/>mTLS
        QueueProxy->>Caikit: gRPC(h2c)/8085<br/>mTLS (Istio sidecar)<br/>Auth: PeerAuthentication STRICT
        Caikit->>TGIS: gRPC/8033 (localhost)<br/>Plaintext (loopback)<br/>Auth: None
        TGIS-->>Caikit: Inference result (gRPC)
        Caikit-->>QueueProxy: gRPC response
        QueueProxy-->>Activator: Response
        Activator-->>Gateway: Response
        Gateway-->>Client: gRPC response (h2)
    end

    rect rgb(255, 240, 220)
        Note over Prometheus,Caikit: Flow 3: Prometheus Metrics Scraping
        Prometheus->>Caikit: GET /metrics<br/>HTTP/8086<br/>PERMISSIVE mTLS<br/>Auth: None
        Caikit-->>Prometheus: Metrics response
    end
